column2: SELECT  b.objra as lam_ra, b.objdec as lam_dec, a.bestobjid as sdss_objid, b.specid, b.teff as lam_teff, b.logg as lam_logg, b.feh as lam_feh, b.rv as lam_rv, a.teffadop as sdss_teff, a.loggadop as sdss_logg, a.fehadop as sdss_feh, a.elodiervfinal as sdss_rv into mydb.cross_dr5_sdss_dr1#_# from  mydb.dt5_# as b CROSS APPLY  dbo.fGetNearestObjEq(b.objra,b.objdec,#) as c join DR1#.sppParams as a on a.bestobjid=c.objid
